58.text:
(a) the Company and its Fund Manager;   
(b) any person employed by or associated with the Company or by the Fund Manager;   
(c) any Director of the Company;   
(d) any person exercising influence over any Director of the Company;   
(e) any body corporate in the same group as the Company;   
(f) any Director of a body corporate referred to in (e);   
(g) any person exercising influence over a body corporate referred to in (e); or (h) the interests of a Shareholder or Creditor of the Company.

88.text:
